创建索引别名
curl -XPUT http://127.0.0.1:9200/markers_v2/_alias/markers

更新索引操作顺序
1.创建新版本索引
2.更新服务端代码
3.重启脚本，脚本向新索引推数据
supervisorctl restart marker2es 
4.别名切换
curl -XPOST "http://127.0.0.1:9200/_aliases" -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '
{
    "actions": [
        { "remove": { "index": "marker_v1", "alias": "markers" }},
        { "add":    { "index": "marker_v2", "alias": "markers" }}
    ]
}
'
5.删除旧索引
删除索引
curl -XDELETE http://127.0.0.1:9200/markers_v2